{"tid":2057241,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"作品曾一度被指「具煽動性」下架　港攝記憑抗爭者傷勢相奪 Sony 世界攝影獎","createTime":"2020-06-09T08:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T04:55:19.000Z","uid":1123,"like":143,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"1a489d9ff1f67b7b0e4ea797d7021f72fb5b2259","tid":2057241,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T08:35:36.000Z","msg":"Sony 世界攝影獎 2020 今日公布得獎名單，香港攝影記者高仲明憑作品「Wounds of Hong Kong」獲得公開賽紀實攝影組冠軍。該輯作品拍攝港人在抗爭中的種種傷勢，惟今年 2 月公布入圍不久，便引發下架風波，主辦方曾指相關影像性質敏感，將作品暫時從網站下架，後來作品重新上架，卻被刪剩四幅。如今，作品獲得紀實攝影組冠軍，「Wounds of Hong Kong」十張照片全部出現在攝影獎官網。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/作品曾一度被指-具煽動性-下架-港攝記憑抗爭者傷勢相奪-sony-世界攝影獎/?fbclid=IwAR2T-XdP41u0wyQok78n2e98phFjX5sKhWRg9reYK49aQ3wQJdbzG1qSK-E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E6%9B%BE%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E5%85%B7%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E6%80%A7-%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6-%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%9D%E8%A8%98%E6%86%91%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E5%82%B7%E5%8B%A2%E7%9B%B8%E5%A5%AA-sony-%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E7%8D%8E%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2T-XdP41u0wyQok78n2e98phFjX5sKhWRg9reYK49aQ3wQJdbzG1qSK-E&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelmhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=183d3de5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fculture%2F%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E6%9B%BE%E4%B8%80%E5%BA%A6%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E5%85%B7%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E6%80%A7-%E4%B8%8B%E6%9E%B6-%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%9D%E8%A8%98%E6%86%91%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E5%82%B7%E5%8B%A2%E7%9B%B8%E5%A5%AA-sony-%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E7%8D%8E%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2T-XdP41u0wyQok78n2e98phFjX5sKhWRg9reYK49aQ3wQJdbzG1qSK-E&h=8c3b6325\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/作品曾一度被指-具煽動性-下架-港攝記憑抗爭者傷勢相奪-sony-世界攝影獎/?fbclid=IwAR2T-XdP41u0wyQok78n2e98phFjX5sKhWRg9reYK49aQ3wQJdbzG1qSK-E</a>"},{"pid":"138c2570601dd95ebff8f6c6febb39d4a4ed5c27","tid":2057241,"uid":7043,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedB